headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Vetir
content:
Calling all recruits: the Vetir is reporting for duty.

Take all the thrills of boot camp out on the open road: the grueling training, the unwavering discipline, the constant selfie taking and bullying of civvies on Bleeter. Only this time, you can take 9 battle buddies with you and bully those civvies in person.

Now available from Warstock.
